{%- comment -%}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BROBASKET HERO REVIEW (W2-03)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Single above-the-fold curated review. Photo + 5 stars + headline + quote + name.

Why hard-coded vs. dynamic (Judge.me): the expert audit flagged that Judge.me's
widget buries the best reviews under a firehose of everything. Hard-coding a hero
review lets us CHOOSE the review that does the most work at the decision moment,
rather than hoping the algorithm surfaces it.

All content is block.settings so James can override per-product in the theme
editor if a product family has a stronger review.

Default content seeded from James's Apr 2026 curation pass:
  * Real review text (shortened)
  * Name changed to a plausible first-name + last-initial
  * Stock photo picker — leave empty to render an initials-circle fallback

Supported block.settings:
  * reviewer_photo   — image_picker  (optional; initials fallback if blank)
  * rating           — range 1–5     (default 5)
  * headline         — text          (default "Best Christmas he's ever had!")
  * quote            — textarea      (the review body)
  * reviewer_name    — text          (default "Sarah M.")
  * review_meta      — text          (default "Verified Customer · December 2025")
  * star_color       — color         (default #F5A623, Google yellow)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign rating      = block.settings.rating        | default: 5 -%}
{%- assign headline    = block.settings.headline      | default: "Best Christmas he's ever had!" -%}
{%- assign quote       = block.settings.quote         | default: "My dad was beyond stoked. He said it was the best Christmas he's ever had. He's 83 and finding gifts he likes is a challenge — thank you for making his day special." -%}
{%- assign name        = block.settings.reviewer_name | default: "Sarah M." -%}
{%- assign meta        = block.settings.review_meta   | default: "Verified Customer" -%}
{%- assign star_color  = block.settings.star_color    | default: "#F5A623" -%}

{%- comment -%} Build initials for fallback avatar {%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign name_parts = name | split: ' ' -%}
{%- capture initials -%}
  {%- for part in name_parts limit: 2 -%}
    {{- part | slice: 0 | upcase -}}
  {%- endfor -%}
{%- endcapture -%}

<figure class="bb-hero-review" style="--bb-hr-star: {{ star_color }};">
  <div class="bb-hero-review__avatar" aria-hidden="true">
    {%- if block.settings.reviewer_photo != blank -%}
      {{ block.settings.reviewer_photo | image_url: width: 160 | image_tag:
          loading: 'lazy',
          widths: '80,120,160',
          sizes: '80px',
          class: 'bb-hero-review__photo',
          alt: name | escape }}
    {%- else -%}
      <span class="bb-hero-review__initials">{{ initials | strip }}</span>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>

  <div class="bb-hero-review__body">
    <div class="bb-hero-review__stars" role="img" aria-label="{{ rating }} out of 5 stars">
      {%- for i in (1..5) -%}
        {%- if i <= rating -%}
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01z"/>
          </svg>
        {%- else -%}
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01z"/>
          </svg>
        {%- endif -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

    {%- if headline != blank -%}
      <p class="bb-hero-review__headline">{{ headline | escape }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}

    <blockquote class="bb-hero-review__quote">
      {{- quote | escape -}}
    </blockquote>

    <figcaption class="bb-hero-review__attribution">
      <span class="bb-hero-review__name">— {{ name | escape }}</span>
      {%- if meta != blank -%}
        <span class="bb-hero-review__meta">{{ meta | escape }}</span>
      {%- endif -%}
    </figcaption>
  </div>
</figure>
